<h1>teaching of biology</h1>
<p>Your work and extracurricular activities indicate that you enjoy explaining ideas or have an interest in contributing to the improvement of our schools. If your passion is getting others excited about biology, teaching may be the path for you.</p>
<p>To become certified to teach biology in a public middle or high school, you can start as an IB major.&nbsp; During your junior year, your major will change to Teaching of Biology, with a minor in Secondary Education. Alternatively, you may earn your master&rsquo;s degree in the Teaching of Biology, after obtaining your bachelor&rsquo;s degree in IB.</p>
